---
import Shell from '../../layouts/dotlocal/Shell.astro'
---

<Shell title="dotlocalctl" description="Backend CLI for dotlocal">
  <div class="container py-[4rem]">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-mono font-bold">dotlocalctl <span class="material-symbols-rounded text-slate-500">terminal</span></h1>

    <p class="text-secondary">
      Backend CLI for <a class="text-blue-500 underline" href="/dotlocal"
        >DotLocal</a
      > written in Rust.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-[3rem]">
      <code class="bg-slate-200 px-2 py-1 rounded-md"
        >brew install dotlocalctl</code>
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-secondary mt-[3rem] mb-4">Description</h2>

    <p>This CLI provides commands to create <code>.local</code> domains and proxies easily.</p>
    <p>Run <code>dotlocalctl --help</code> for available commands and parameters</p>
  </div>
</Shell>
